  "backstory": {
    "personalityTraits": "Acts like a cat, at one moment could be your friend, the next could be completely unpredictable. He wants to do good most of the time, just can be persuaded into sowing chaos",
    "ideals": "He used to be a musician, the heart of a party. The sex icon. All the warm bodies and good drinks he could want, but he\u2019s well past his prime. Most people wouldn\u2019t recognize him now adays. But he doesn\u2019t hold ill will, he just wants some of that money and glory back",
    "bonds": "His cat Juno, his dog Cleo, and his niece Jane. Her bother Chet is accepted by James but he\u2019s not fond of his carefree lifestyle",
    "flaws": "He has massive nerve damage. He can only feel pain in his shoulder. Able to do a lot if you are able to direct or focus him, as he\u2019s not able to resist temptations",
